prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D comic book style artwork for a birthday card front. Grandpa and Tong Tong from the reference photo are transformed into illustrated comic book characters. Grandpa is the hero, depicted in a powerful and loving pose at the helm of a stylized traditional Chinese boat. He is wearing his grey turtleneck and jeans from the photo. Tong Tong, in their red patterned sweater, stands proudly beside him, looking up at him with admiration. The background is a dynamic comic book splash page, split into dramatic panels. One panel explodes with vibrant imagery of Chinese opera masks with dramatic expressions and flowing ribbons. Another panel showcases a bountiful, colorful display of seafood like crabs, lobsters, and fish, rendered with bold ink lines. The main scene on the boat is set against a backdrop of stylized ocean waves and a radiant sunburst. The overall composition is dynamic, with action lines and a vibrant, warm color palette of reds, golds, and deep blues. In the center, the text "Happy Birthday, Grandpa" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, glowing slightly. The entire scene is framed with a thin, bold ink border typical of comic books.
